'''湯浅年子'''（{{bd|1909年|12月11日|1980年|2月1日}}）是一位在法國工作的日本[[核子物理|核子物理]]學家，也是日本首位女性物理學者。<ref name="aapps">{{Cite journal|url = http://www.cospa.ntu.edu.tw/aappsbulletin/data/17-4/17_4_p1517.pdf|journal = AAPPS Bulletin|date = August 2007|volume = 17|issue = 4|title = Toshiko Yuasa (1909-80): the First Japanese Woman Physicist and Her Followers in Japan|first1 = Eri|last1 = Yagi|first2 = Hisako|last2 = Matsuda|pages = 15-17|accessdate = 6 November 2015}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
湯浅年子生於1909年的東京[[台東區|台東區]]<ref name="ocha">{{Cite web|url = http://archives.cf.ocha.ac.jp/en/researcher/yuasa_toshiko.html|title = Toshiko Yuasa (1909~1980)|publisher = [[Ochanomizu_University|Ochanomizu University]]|accessdate = 6 November 2015}}</ref> 她的父親是日本[[特許廳_(日本)|特許廳]]的工程師，母親則來自傳統文學世家。<ref name="aapps">{{Cite journal|url = http://www.cospa.ntu.edu.tw/aappsbulletin/data/17-4/17_4_p1517.pdf|journal = AAPPS Bulletin|date = August 2007|volume = 17|issue = 4|title = Toshiko Yuasa (1909-80): the First Japanese Woman Physicist and Her Followers in Japan|first1 = Eri|last1 = Yagi|first2 = Hisako|last2 = Matsuda|pages = 15-17|accessdate = 6 November 2015}}</ref> 1927年至1931年間，湯浅就讀於東京女子高等師範學校（現[[御茶水女子大學|御茶水女子大學]]）理科<ref name="ocha">{{Cite web|url = http://archives.cf.ocha.ac.jp/en/researcher/yuasa_toshiko.html|title = Toshiko Yuasa (1909~1980)|publisher = [[Ochanomizu_University|Ochanomizu University]]|accessdate = 6 November 2015}}</ref> ，隨後進入[[筑波大學|筑波大學]]，攻讀物理學，是日本第一個專研物理學的女性。<ref>{{Cite book|last1 = Kodate|first1 = Naonori|last2 = Kodate|first2 = Kashiko|title = Japanese Women in Science and Engineering: History and Policy Change|url = http://books.google.com/books?id=i6ZGCgAAQBAJ&pg=PR53|year = 2015|publisher = Taylor & Francis|isbn = 978-1-317-59504-5|page = 53}}</ref> 1934年，湯浅自筑波大學畢業，取得理學士學位<ref name="ocha">{{Cite web|url = http://archives.cf.ocha.ac.jp/en/researcher/yuasa_toshiko.html|title = Toshiko Yuasa (1909~1980)|publisher = [[Ochanomizu_University|Ochanomizu University]]|accessdate = 6 November 2015}}</ref>

== 職業生涯 ==
畢業後，湯浅任教於Tokyo Bunrika University，為兼任助理教授，開始研究分子光譜學。1935年，湯浅轉為[[東京女子大學|東京女子大學]]講師，任教至1937年，之後幾年則返回母校東京女子高等師範學校任教，擔任助理教授。<ref name="haines">{{Cite book|last = Haines|first = Catharine M. C.|title = International Women in Science: A Biographical Dictionary to 1950|url = http://books.google.com/books?id=HftdjMNDvwIC&pg=PA342|year = 2001|publisher = ABC-CLIO|isbn = 978-1-57607-090-1|pages = 341–342}}</ref>

